==English==
===Etymology===
From the brown paper bag traditionally used to carry one's own [[lunch]] from home.

===Noun===
'''[[brown]] [[bag]]'''
# {{idiom}} A short [[presentation]] or [[seminar]] on a given subject, especially one given at [[lunchtime]].
#:''Did you attend the '''brown bag''' Tuesday on healthy exercise habits?''

===Verb===
'''brown bag'''
#To carry one's lunch from home, as in a bag, rather than purchase it from a cafeteria or restaurant.